4.9 Inspecting values: the Inspector structure

inspectIt

Function

Structure

Shell.Inspector

Type

val inspectIt: unit -> unit

Syntax

inspectIt: () -> ()

Arguments

()

Values

()

Description

Invokes the TTY inspector tool on the value of it. If there is no method for displaying this type, then the exception LookupValId is raised.
